Class DocumentType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ecoinformatics.seek.ecogrid.DocumentType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SelectableDocumentType

    public class DocumentType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class express a DocumentType object. It has three filed. The namespace - the document type The label - readable name for namespace The metadataSepecificationClass - a java class implemented for this namespace
    Author:
    Jing Tao
